1. Nf3 f5 2. d3 d6 {[%cal Be7e5] Black wants to play e5!} 3. e4 {Strike the 
center, in order to make use of the delay in Black's development because of 1. 
...f5.} e5 4. Nc3 Nc6 ({The main course spends 6 variations on} 4... Nc6 {.}) 5. 
